thread.title: Gisela Schmid

author: Gisela Schmid
title: Gisela Schmid
text: We selected Salmon and chicken, 2 different dishes, a little more pricy than others. It was well worth it. The food was delicious. Warm up time in oven was longer than indicated, so that was a learning experience, no big deal. The portions were plentiful. As a first time customer, we were treated to a very tasty lemon-poppy muffin. We will definitely order again.
